00:04:01.949 --> 00:04:07.469
an appointment with government officials to promote a more tolerant attitude of Jehovah's

00:04:07.469 --> 00:04:12.189
organization and the work that Jehovah's Witnesses were doing in Eastern Europe, and especially

00:04:12.189 --> 00:04:19.389
in Poland. Now mind you, this was all taking place some 10 years prior to the fall of communism

00:04:19.389 --> 00:04:25.069
in Eastern Europe. They took various steps to meet with the local brothers in person,

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:30.509
