00:04:30.509 --> 00:04:36.589
city of Leningrad with Brother Kose, who was responsible for the activity in the territory. Brother Kose

00:04:36.670 --> 00:04:41.790
said that he received tremendous encouragement from that discussion, from the conversation with Brother

00:04:41.790 --> 00:04:48.750
Barry. And it was interesting that it wasn't until after that meeting that Brother Kose found out

00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:54.750
that he had been talking to a member of the governing body. The brothers in Eastern Europe really

00:04:54.750 --> 00:05:01.230
needed help to resist decades of satanic efforts to destroy their fate in Jehovah, and weaken the

00:05:01.230 --> 00:05:08.029
unity and confidence in his organization. And the members of the governing body showed a very

00:05:08.029 --> 00:05:16.430
deep appreciation for the brothers who kept the communication to the brothers behind the iron

00:05:16.430 --> 00:05:22.829
curtain, because you have to imagine how to get the spiritual food there. They had to be willing

00:05:22.829 --> 00:05:33.629
